name: Ikaros - Heaven's Lost Property
description:
Ikaros from Heaven's Lost Property (Sora no Otoshimono).

Use "Ikaros" as the prompt, best paired with "shoulder armor" and "open clothes"

Used with 0.8-1.0 weight, your results may vary,

Comments and shared gens appreciated! May work on a second version if interest is there.

This will tend to favor NSFW, even without NSFW prompts.

modelVersions.name: Ikaros v2
modelVersions.description:
New version trained on NovelAI and additional images.

Use "typealpha" for her Angeloid armor, you can try combining it with Ikaros but I think typealpha alone works better for how I have this tagged.

Hopefully those who have been waiting for Version 2 enjoys it!

Please comment, like, and share your gens! :) I appreciate all reviews/responses.
